{
  "name": "PATCH_sso-teammates-username",
  "description": "**This endpoint allows you to modify an existing SSO Teammate.**\n\nTo turn a teammate into an admin, the request body should contain the `is_admin` field set to `true`. Otherwise, set `is_admin` to false and pass in all the scopes that a teammate should have.\n\nOnly the parent user and Teammates with admin permissions can update another Teammate’s permissions. Admin users can only update permissions.",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "username": {
        "format": "email",
        "type": "string",
        "description": "This email address must be the same address assigned to the teammate in your IdP"
      },
      "body": {
        "example": {
          "email": "jane_doe@example.com",
          "first_name": "Jane",
          "is_admin": false,
          "last_name": "Doe",
          "scopes": [
            "mail.batch.create",
            "mail.batch.delete",
            "mail.batch.read",
            "mail.batch.update",
            "mail.send"
          ]
        },
        "properties": {
          "first_name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "is_admin": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "last_name": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "scopes": {
            "items": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "type": "array"
          }
        },
        "type": "object"
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "username"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "PATCH",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "http://api.sendgrid.com/v3/sso/teammates/{username}"
    },
    "body": {
      "$": "body",
      "encode": "json"
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Single Sing-On Teammate Common Fields"
        },
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**email**",
            "**first_name**: The Teammate’s first name.",
            "**is_admin**: Indicates if the Teammate has admin permissions.",
            "**is_read_only**: Indicates if the Teammate has read_only permissions.",
            "**last_name**: The Teammate’s last name.",
            "**is_sso**: Indicates if the Teammate authenticates with SendGrid using SSO or with a username and password.",
            "**username**: This should be set to the Teammate's email address.",
            "**address**: The Teammate’s street address.",
            "**address2**: The Teammate’s apartment number, suite number, or other secondary address information that is not part of the physical street address.",
            "**city**: The Teammate's city.",
            "**company**: The Teammate’s company name.",
            "**country**: The Teammate’s country of residence.",
            "**phone**: The Teammate’s stored phone number.",
            "**scopes**: The permission scopes assigned to the Teammate.",
            "**state**: The Teammate’s state or province.",
            "**user_type**: A Teammate can be an “admin,” “owner,” or “teammate.” Each role is associated with the scope of the Teammate’s permissions.",
            "**website**: A website associated with the Teammate",
            "**zip**: The Teammate’s zip code."
          ]
        },
        {
          "$lang": "json",
          "$code": {
            "$encode": "json",
            "$indent": true,
            "$content": {
              "$": "$.body"
            }
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    "400": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
